  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.736,
      "end": 1.28,
      "text": "CHAPTER VII."
    },
    {
      "start": 1.74,
      "end": 4.04,
      "text": "OF ALICE'S ADVENTURES IN WONDERLAND."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.32,
      "end": 5.0,
      "text": "By Lewis Carroll."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.04,
      "end": 8.4,
      "text": "This LibriVox recording is in the public domain.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 9.6,
      "end": 10.9,
      "text": "A MAD TEA-PARTY",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 12.94,
      "end": 15.78,
      "text": "There was a table set out under a tree in front of the house,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 15.94,
      "end": 17.28,
      "text": "and the March Hare and"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.28,
      "end": 18.9,
      "text": "the Hatter were having tea at it."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.36,
      "end": 20.92,
      "text": "a Dormouse was sitting between them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.0,
      "end": 21.56,
      "text": "fast asleep,"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.76,
      "end": 23.8,
      "text": "and the other two were using it as"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.8,
      "end": 24.2,
      "text": "a cushion"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.32,
      "end": 25.58,
      "text": "resting their elbows on it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.6,
      "end": 27.14,
      "text": "and talking over its head."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.608,
      "end": 30.34,
      "text": "\"Very uncomfortable for the Dormouse,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 30.46,
      "end": 30.9,
      "text": "thought Alice;"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.1,
      "end": 32.32,
      "text": "\"only as it's asleep,"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.5,
      "end": 33.74,
      "text": "suppose it doesn't mind.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 34.46,
      "end": 36.18,
      "text": "The table was a large one,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 36.34,
      "end": 39.4,
      "text": "but the three were all crowded together at one corner of it."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.06,
      "end": 40.48,
      "text": "\"No room!"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.64,
      "end": 41.14,
      "text": "No room!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 41.34,
      "end": 43.32,
      "text": "they cried out when they saw Alice coming."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.32,
      "end": 45.32,
      "text": "\"There's _plenty_ of room!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 45.52,
      "end": 46.64,
      "text": "said Alice indignantly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.74,
      "end": 50.26,
      "text": "and she sat down in a large arm-chair at one end of the table."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.576,
      "end": 53.32,
      "text": "\"Have some wine,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 53.82,
      "end": 55.82,
      "text": "the March Hare said in an encouraging tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.67,
      "end": 58.6,
      "text": "Alice looked all round the table,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 58.68,
      "end": 60.4,
      "text": "but there was nothing on it but tea."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.22,
      "end": 62.2,
      "text": "\"I don't see any wine,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 62.34,
      "end": 63.0,
      "text": "she remarked."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.78,
      "end": 64.5,
      "text": "\"There isn't any,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 64.7,
      "end": 65.6,
      "text": "said the March Hare."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.56,
      "end": 68.68,
      "text": "\"Then it wasn't very civil of you to offer it,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 68.82,
      "end": 69.96,
      "text": "said Alice angrily."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.14,
      "end": 74.08,
      "text": "\"It wasn't very civil of you to sit down without being invited,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 74.46,
      "end": 75.3,
      "text": "said the March Hare."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.66,
      "end": 78.34,
      "text": "\"I didn't know it was _your_ table,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 78.52,
      "end": 79.02,
      "text": "said Alice;"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.456,
      "end": 81.2,
      "text": "\"it's laid for a great many more than three.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 82.72,
      "end": 83.96,
      "text": "\"Your hair wants cutting,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 84.16,
      "end": 84.8,
      "text": "said the Hatter."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.12,
      "end": 88.24,
      "text": "He had been looking at Alice for some time with great curiosity,"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.56,
      "end": 90.42,
      "text": "and this was his first speech."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.14,
      "end": 93.88,
      "text": "\"You should learn not to make personal remarks,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 94.28,
      "end": 95.54,
      "text": "Alice said with some severity;"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.1,
      "end": 96.74,
      "text": "\"it's very rude.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 97.9,
      "end": 100.8,
      "text": "The Hatter opened his eyes very wide on hearing this;",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 100.86,
      "end": 102.62,
      "text": "but all he _said_ was"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.2,
      "end": 105.32,
      "text": "\"Why is a raven like a writing-desk?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 106.6,
      "end": 106.84,
      "text": "\"Come,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 107.04,
      "end": 108.16,
      "text": "we shall have some fun now!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 108.24,
      "end": 108.74,
      "text": "thought Alice."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.3,
      "end": 110.82,
      "text": "\"I'm glad they've begun asking riddles.--"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.0,
      "end": 113.14,
      "text": "I believe I can guess that,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 113.22,
      "end": 113.9,
      "text": "she added aloud."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.9,
      "end": 117.04,
      "text": "\"Do you mean that you think you can find",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 117.04,
      "end": 119.0,
      "text": "out the answer to it?\" said the March Hare."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.776,
      "end": 121.06,
      "text": "\"Exactly so,\" said Alice.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 122.56,
      "end": 125.38,
      "text": "\"Then you should say what you mean,\" the March Hare went on.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 126.54,
      "end": 128.18,
      "text": "\"I do,\" Alice hastily replied;",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 128.68,
      "end": 130.86,
      "text": "\"at least--at least I mean what I say"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.0,
      "end": 132.576,
      "text": "--that's the same thing, you know.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 133.696,
      "end": 135.72,
      "text": "\"Not the same thing a bit!\" said the Hatter.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 136.08,
      "end": 136.36,
      "text": "\"Why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.42,
      "end": 138.84,
      "text": "you might just as well say that 'I see what I"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.84,
      "end": 141.94,
      "text": "eat' is the same thing as 'I eat what I see'!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 142.74,
      "end": 145.12,
      "text": "\"You might just as well say,\" added the March Hare,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 145.66,
      "end": 149.38,
      "text": "\"that 'I like what I get' is the same thing as 'I get what I like'!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 150.368,
      "end": 153.26,
      "text": "\"You might just as well say,\" added the Dormouse,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 153.4,
      "end": 155.32,
      "text": "which seemed to be talking in his sleep,"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.0,
      "end": 157.9,
      "text": "\"that 'I breathe when I sleep' is the"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.9,
      "end": 160.704,
      "text": "same thing as 'I sleep when I breathe'!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 162.52,
      "end": 164.92,
      "text": "\"It _is_ the same thing with you,\" said the Hatter;",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 165.6,
      "end": 167.26,
      "text": "and here the conversation dropped,"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.64,
      "end": 169.46,
      "text": "and the party sat silent for a minute,"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.66,
      "end": 171.56,
      "text": "while Alice thought over all she could"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.56,
      "end": 173.48,
      "text": "remember about ravens and writing-desks,"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.92,
      "end": 174.62,
      "text": "which wasn't much."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.58,
      "end": 178.08,
      "text": "The Hatter was the first to break the silence.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 178.66,
      "end": 180.0,
      "text": "\"What day of the month is it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 180.1,
      "end": 180.56,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.72,
      "end": 181.46,
      "text": "turning to Alice:"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.66,
      "end": 184.46,
      "text": "he had taken his watch out of his"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.46,
      "end": 186.43,
      "text": "pocket, and was looking at it uneasily,"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.8,
      "end": 189.32,
      "text": "shaking it every now and then, and holding it to his ear."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.104,
      "end": 192.9,
      "text": "Alice considered a little, and then said",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 193.38,
      "end": 193.74,
      "text": "\"The fourth.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 194.944,
      "end": 195.8,
      "text": "\"Two days wrong!\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 196.12,
      "end": 196.82,
      "text": "sighed the Hatter."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.1,
      "end": 199.1,
      "text": "\"I told you butter would not suit the works!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 199.58,
      "end": 199.68,
      "text": "he added,"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.02,
      "end": 201.5,
      "text": "looking angrily at the March Hare."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.38,
      "end": 203.78,
      "text": "\"It was the _best_ butter,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 204.0,
      "end": 205.56,
      "text": "the March Hare meekly replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.42,
      "end": 206.74,
      "text": "\"Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 206.8,
      "end": 208.74,
      "text": "but some crumbs must have got in as well,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 208.98,
      "end": 209.74,
      "text": "the Hatter grumbled:"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.22,
      "end": 212.02,
      "text": "\"you shouldn't have put it in with the bread-knife.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 213.82,
      "end": 216.24,
      "text": "The March Hare took the watch and looked at it gloomily:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 216.84,
      "end": 219.78,
      "text": "then he dipped it into his cup of tea, and looked at it again:"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.3,
      "end": 222.96,
      "text": "but he could think of nothing better to say than his first remark,"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.56,
      "end": 224.94,
      "text": "\"It was the _best_ butter,"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.02,
      "end": 225.3,
      "text": "you know.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 226.592,
      "end": 229.12,
      "text": "Alice had been looking over his shoulder with some curiosity.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 229.58,
      "end": 231.36,
      "text": "\"What a funny watch!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 231.64,
      "end": 232.34,
      "text": "she remarked."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.54,
      "end": 235.58,
      "text": "\"It tells the day of the month, and doesn't tell what o'clock it is!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 237.08,
      "end": 237.86,
      "text": "\"Why should it?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 237.92,
      "end": 238.54,
      "text": "muttered the Hatter."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.22,
      "end": 241.36,
      "text": "\"Does _your_ watch tell you what year it is?\""
    }
  ]
}